NC0235: (fi) selite muutettu: general:
If preferential code indicating quota [x20, x25, x28] THEN Quota order number = R, ELSE cannot be used. &#8594; JOS tietoelementin {{FIe-180}} kaksi viimeistГӨ numeroa ovat JOUKOSSA {20, 25, 28}
  NIIN {{FIe-187}} = 'R'
MUUTEN {{FIe-187}} = 'N', (sv) selite muutettu: general:
If preferential code indicating quota [x20, x25, x28] THEN Quota order number = R, ELSE cannot be used. &#8594; OM tvГҘ sista siffrorna i {{FIe-180}} ГӨr i GRUPPEN {20, 25, 28}
  DГ… ГӨr {{FIe-187}} = 'R'
ANNARS ГӨr {{FIe-187}} = 'N', (en) selite muutettu: general:
If preferential code indicating quota [x20, x25, x28] THEN Quota order number = R, ELSE cannot be used. &#8594; IF the last two digits in {{FIe-180}} are in SET {20, 25, 28}
  THEN {{FIe-187}} = 'R'
