NR0061: (fi) selite muutettu: import:
If declaration is standard customs declaration (FI415) and previous procedure is 10,
then if case is customs warehousing declarations (requested procedure 71), previous document type must be type one of  N337, N355, N825, N820, N821, N952, 1ZZZ,
        else the  previous document type must be one of  N337, N355, N825, N820, N821, N952, 1ZZZ or 1781.

